{"tid":1554462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"薄扶林道21歲女途人捱新巴撞 重創送院不治　","createTime":"2019-09-09T03:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T03:51:39.000Z","uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3404777f92d3935cdfa0ba375b308a7b0a6e91f5","tid":1554462,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:48:01.000Z","msg":"香港仔薄扶林道薄扶林公眾騎術學校對開，早上10時19分，一輛小巴沿慢線行駛，其間一名21歲女途人過馬路，小巴停下讓其過路，惟女途人行至快線，一部新巴駛至收掣不及，撞倒該名過路女子，女途人飛彈8米，倒卧路中，重創昏迷，新巴再駛前4米始停下，巴士擋風玻璃爆裂，地面遺下一灘血迹及傷者的眼鏡，女傷者送院，經搶救後不治，警方正調查意外原因，新巴車長涉危險駕駛導致他人死亡被捕帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190909/60025284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F60025284&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kRSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=6e6e70a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F60025284&h=f3d5092e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190909/60025284</a>"},{"pid":"a2f7f2c68b09ab04a526826e68c9b0d744c7fb44","tid":1554462,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T03:51:39.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港政府打壓集會自由，阻止市民向美國請願。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}